c.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/1b571f99316f420c6b5c2e62b638d91e.webm?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/1b571f99316f420c6b5c2e62b638d91e.mp4?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PHYSICS THAT HIT HARD:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Next-Gen Soft-Body:</strong> Everything jiggles, shakes, and reacts to touch exactly as nature (and magic) intended. No stiffness here – just pure, soft physics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grab the Wand:</strong> Literally. Full manual control. Thanks to precise collisions, you enter where you want, how you want, and at what pace you want. You are in charge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Automation for the lazy:</strong> Hands tired from &quot;adventuring&quot;? Activate auto-modes, set the speed, and enjoy the view.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/cddfa1b8674f4b4260a5c16d819fd8ca.poster.avif?t=1771343422\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/cddfa1b8674f4b4260a5c16d819fd8ca.webm?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/cddfa1b8674f4b4260a5c16d819fd8ca.mp4?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>YOU ARE THE GAME MASTER:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Telekinesis &amp; &quot;Dolls&quot;:</strong> Magic is power. Grab a girl with telekinesis, lift her, move her, bend her limbs. You set the scene for yourself – literally.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magic Eye:</strong> Want a front-row view? Launch the flying eye, fly it right into the center of the action, and watch details on the Magic Mirror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mood on demand:</strong> Is the graveyard too scary? Change the lighting with one click and set the mood for a romantic encounter... or a hardcore exorcism.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/045c0cca8788622d73abbd6ff65bb935.poster.avif?t=1771343422\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/045c0cca8788622d73abbd6ff65bb935.webm?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/045c0cca8788622d73abbd6ff65bb935.mp4?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Unique locations. Many positions. One goal. Go for it, Champion.</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>&quot;A plague... The women of this realm are burning, and not from dragon fire.&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/58924305dfaa0968f10ca93d0de240a4.poster.avif?t=1771343422\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/58924305dfaa0968f10ca93d0de240a4.webm?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/web