<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/cddfa1b8674f4b4260a5c16d819fd8ca.poster.avif?t=1771343422\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/cddfa1b8674f4b4260a5c16d819fd8ca.webm?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/cddfa1b8674f4b4260a5c16d819fd8ca.mp4?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>YOU ARE THE GAME MASTER:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Telekinesis &amp; &quot;Dolls&quot;:</strong> Magic is power. Grab a girl with telekinesis, lift her, move her, bend her limbs. You set the scene for yourself – literally.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magic Eye:</strong> Want a front-row view? Launch the flying eye, fly it right into the center of the action, and watch details on the Magic Mirror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mood on demand:</strong> Is the graveyard too scary? Change the lighting with one click and set the mood for a romantic encounter... or a hardcore exorcism.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/045c0cca8788622d73abbd6ff65bb935.poster.avif?t=1771343422\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/045c0cca8788622d73abbd6ff65bb935.webm?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/extras/045c0cca8788622d73abbd6ff65bb935.mp4?t=1771343422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Unique locations. Many positions. One goal. Go for it, Champion.</strong></p>", "short_description": "An adult fantasy where you leave the steel sword at home. Your &quot;Wand&quot; is the only cure for a magical fever. A VR game with insane soft-body physics, telekinesis, and total freedom. Cure them all... deeply.", "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong>, French, Italian, German, Spanish - Spain, Arabic, Bulgarian, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Czech, Danish, Finnish, Greek, Spanish - Latin America, Dutch, Indonesian, Japanese, Korean, Norwegian, Polish, Portuguese - Portugal, Portuguese - Brazil, Russian, Romanian, Swedish, Thai, Turkish, Ukrainian, Vietnamese, Hungarian<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/a769db28cc41b93d3c2890184eec738a79ebec38/header.jpg?t=1771343422", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/55d4613fbe5f7a141fbd88d6f2be5031660c7d20/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1771343422", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3868770/55d4613fbe5f7a141fbd88d6f2be5031660c7d20/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1771343422", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>OS:</strong> Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i5-6600 (or equivalent)<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 16 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GeForce RTX 3060 (or equivalent)<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 15 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>VR Support:</strong> SteamVR</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><